"string name="open_in_browser" is of no help, but at-least that has to change for it have any hopes of landing on web- between all the translated languages. Or a comment. Comments don't change existing translations though.
Edit: I see a lot of "Browser" in https://hosted.weblate.org/translate/newpipe/strings/nb_NO/?checksum=7f6f1617954bdd58 which is not correct in Italian, but not the 5 languages I checked, and not in Danish either.

